%%! title: "%use"

%{! A **``%use``** directive adds a [constraint domain](/wiki/constraint-domain/) to the current Twelf [signature](/wiki/twelf-signature/). 

Like some other directives, for instance [``%clause``](/wiki/percent-clause/), it is incompatible with Twelf's ability to verify [totality assertions](/wiki/totality-assertion/) and [metatheorems](/wiki/metatheorem/).

## See also

* [Constraint domains](/wiki/constraint-domain/)
* \{\{guide|chapter=6|section=32|title=Constraint domains\}\}

\{\{keyword|key=use\}\} !}%

